# Alfred sync-folder contents are committed so preferences travel with dotfiles.
#
# WARNING: workflow folders under Alfred.alfredpreferences/workflows/ can embed
# API keys, tokens, and other credentials in their info.plist / config files.
# Scrub any secrets before committing, or keep sensitive workflows out of sync.

# Machine-local preferences (per-machine state, not meant to be shared).
Alfred.alfredpreferences/preferences/local/
